-- First Foreign Planes Arrive in Israel to Help Put Out Fires That Killed 40
-- B y   C a l e v   B e n - D a v i d
-- 2010-12-03T05:03:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-03/first-foreign-planes-arrive-in-israel-to-help-put-out-fires-that-killed-40.html
One plane from Greece and one from
Bulgaria landed in Israel this morning with men and equipment to
hel contain forest fires raging in the hills outside Haifa that
have claimed 40 lives, an Israeli Army spokeswomen said,
speaking anonymously according to military regulation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
